    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "与大夫对饮在临江亭上",
        "关羽",
        "叫人来看大杯把酒献上",
        "周仓",
        "周泰",
        "四水手",
        "想当年破黄巾东除西荡",
        "数十载动干戈未离马上",
        "甘宁",
        "盖世功劳人钦仰",
        "蒋钦",
        "陈武",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、甘宁、鲁肃、周仓、关羽同上。关羽、鲁肃同入座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯驾到，肃未曾远迎，望祈恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某家久未致候，大夫海涵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫招宴，足见故人情义。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宴齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆宴！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖细吹打〗。鲁肃送酒入坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻君侯海量，今日定要尽醉方休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叨扰了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日里与大夫共饮琼浆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在筵前听关某诉一诉衷肠："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "战吕布诛文丑刀斩颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉主命统雄兵坐镇荆襄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙厚意备酒宴甚是叨光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当年破黄巾东除西荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "数十载动干戈未离马上"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "与大夫对饮在临江亭上"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "君侯说话太谦让，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "鲁肃言来细端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "灭黄巾破吕布天下名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙大驾临东吴日月增光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当年破黄巾东除西荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "数十载动干戈未离马上"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "与大夫对饮在临江亭上"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯辱临，定要畅饮一回。想当年君侯辞曹以后，过五关、斩六将，单骑千里"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之事，可能说与肃一听否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盖世功劳人钦仰"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫人来看大杯把酒献上"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫不嫌絮烦，听某道来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔慢板） 想当年在曹营多安享，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为寻兄长出许昌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沿途关口动刀枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩福、王植马前亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三尺剑劈卞喜他命丧佛堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青龙刀斩鼠辈命丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擂鼓三通斩蔡阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯武艺无敌，其乃天神降世也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔慢板） 似这等神威勇无人能挡，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "博得美名天下扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊君侯，肃有一言，不知当讲不当讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何金言，但讲不妨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当年皇叔借去我国荆州，屯军养马。那时也曾言道，日后得了西川，即将荆"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "州还我东吴。前次诸葛瑾先生由西川归来，奉皇叔之命，领取荆州，君侯却再"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三不与，不知是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫，今日饮宴，乃是朋友之情，军国大事，何须提起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这！还要君侯裁夺！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小锣〗，〖作刀鸣声〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！君侯这是什么响亮！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是某宝刀的啸声！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是君侯的刀啸？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知这刀，几年一啸？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自桃园结义以来，某家即有此刀，数十馀年，直到今日它只啸了三次。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知刀啸主何吉凶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不过是杀人而已。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何以见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一次刀啸，应在斩颜良、诛文丑；第二次刀啸应在过五关斩六将；今日这第"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三次刀啸么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽视鲁肃佯笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只恐怕要应在大夫你的身上了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃吓倒，四龙套同扶起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周仓，刀来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽持酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀哇，青龙刀！想你随某出兵多年，也不知斩了多少上将。今日鲁大夫设宴相"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邀，在临江亭上散酒，你也来饮上一杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽泼酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青龙偃月白光凝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能征惯战血染红！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯再饮几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒已够了，某家要告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽接刀、拉鲁肃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙大夫情意厚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尽欢而醉意悠悠！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常言三杯和万事，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一醉便能解千愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽佯醉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关某要告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "送君侯！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、甘宁、鲁肃、周仓、关羽同转场。四水手同暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭了扶手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四水手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、周仓同上船。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫，某深感盛情，多谢了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（开船。四水手、周仓、关羽同下。陈武、甘宁、蒋钦、周泰同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、甘宁、蒋钦、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫，为何将关羽放走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位将军哪！看那关羽虽然言语和悦，却面带杀气，他提刀在手，我若一言动"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手，他必先杀我鲁肃啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、甘宁、蒋钦、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计岂不是又不成了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃叹气。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、蒋钦、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不若我等驾起船只，领兵追赶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
